data.description: A true gem nestled behind the private gates of Myakka River Trails sits this custom-built masterpiece where luxury, elegance, and the natural beauty of over 7 acres converge in perfect harmony.   This stunning home boasts four bedrooms, three bathrooms, a den/office, and a bonus room, offering spacious living and endless possibilities. 8-foot doors, crown molding, soaring ceilings, along with many architectural upgrades can be found throughout, captivating you with its sophistication.  The heart of this home is undoubtedly the open kitchen and family room, designed with entertaining in mind. The kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, including a GE Monogram 6-burner gas stove, a center island with a bar sink, a built-in wine rack, and more. With an eat-in kitchen and breakfast bar areas, it's a culinary enthusiast's dream.  The family room is both voluminous and inviting, with a built-in entertainment center and a two-sided fireplace that can also be enjoyed in the spacious bonus/sitting room. The entire space exudes warmth and comfort, making it perfect for gatherings of family and friends.  The master suite is a sanctuary of its own, offering two walk-in closets with built-in shelving and a master bathroom ensuite that leaves nothing to be desired. His and her vanities, water closets, and showers are flooded in natural light and elevate your daily routines to a new level of luxury.  This home is not just a masterpiece indoors, but also outdoors. Step onto the expansive lanai and you'll be greeted by an infinity/negative edge pool that appears to merge seamlessly with your very own private lake. The ClearVue pool screening ensures uninterrupted views of the surrounding beauty. Whether you're relaxing under the covered lanai or taking a dip in the pool, this space is an oasis of tranquility.  For those who appreciate the practicalities of life, this home has it all. A whole-house generator, RO system, double-pane thermal windows, and central vacuum system are just a few of the thoughtful features that make daily living effortless and enjoyable.  With an oversized three-car garage that includes golf cart parking and its own separate entrance, this property has tons of space! Location, Location, Location!! Minutes to Wellen Park, Cool Today Braves Stadium, I-75, Beaches and so much more!!  Upon the completion of River Road, there will be a path for biking, golf carts and walking too!
